   LA-LAWSUITS (Los Angeles) _ When it comes to defending the city
against personal injury and liability lawsuits, City Hall's chief
lawyer acts as if ignorance is an important part of an effective
defense. By Deborah Sullivan. (Will move in the ``n'' California
news file.)
